Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  會長就沒有不睏的早上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡了幾個小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jennifer一直都是這麼說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「睡眠不足可是美容的大敵」喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  摯愛的Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那如絲般潤滑的肌膚  I wanna touch you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明愛理他們馬上就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有大人物要來視察嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎  愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  詩織阿姨  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您這是要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  休息日加班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  你就是KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who is it？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨  佳織的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really！？  不是sister嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎  愛理  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  難得來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們慢慢玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  都來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  都買來了哦  牛奶和雞蛋還有奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要這些就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  別的都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是文化節上用的點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什麼點心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為必須提前一天先做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能做些簡單的烤製點心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要做  就認真嘗試看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑是佳織親手做的這一點  粉絲們肯定會絡繹不絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角不是天象儀嗎  咖啡廳只是順帶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩邊都是主角啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出來的點心也是越好吃越好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你會做點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好失禮啊  別看我這樣手還是很靈巧的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是沒有做過而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽著佳織的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是佳織  你手腕的傷沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是像平常一樣用的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了  結說一會她也會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川要來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不過凪沙學姐好像有事來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺要變熱鬧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結知道來我家的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且把地圖發給凪沙學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西有必要非得自己做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天象儀什麼的  店裡買個不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  這樣說的話點心也可以去店裡買
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不就沒有存在的價值了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  累死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹了連半小時都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不擅長這種平凡的活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  反正開始就沒指望過你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Treasure…get！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:05:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼大不了的嘛  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先做的已經烤好啦  想讓你們嘗一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸展運動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scone！這玩意看起來好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好試驗品一號剛烤好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結也來嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就去倒點紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是走著來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  因為天氣非常好順便能光合作用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是日光浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜  要是凪沙學姐也在的話全員就能湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙學姐好像過一會也能來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  誰讓你隨便開始吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  不是要試吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這只是偷吃而已吧  不給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦  還有好多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織是Angel啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我  做的真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大部份都是佳織做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也撒了粉  做了形狀的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這個能成為天文學會的招牌商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  先定下來把這個加入菜單  接下來還要再加幾個別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來想試著做下小餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結能來一起幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結會燒飯做菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我來教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要這樣來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要用那個來開星座的小洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  用微妙的大小區別來調整通光量從而再現星空的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心謹慎才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概要開多少個洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少個呢  肉眼能看到的星星大概有數千個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus  好蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤好要多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三四分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會能借用一些時間嗎  有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼  在我面前不能說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等那邊烤好了再說行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  那就一會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲  這個模特的腰部曲線和Jennifer一模一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了  尾宿八做的太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就行了嘛  那種東西沒人會在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！說不定就會有對觀星非常感興趣的人來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有更好用的工具就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色也想好好再現一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  烤的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子就不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  畢竟第一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？結呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊  是不是去廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後一定會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  結  餅乾烤好了哦  來嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  結也說好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  我也再來一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  成功了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦  這邊只能我自己做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試驗品二號做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈  等死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像形狀各異啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是試驗品了啊  快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天應該能做的差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要踩那裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往乏味的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也嘗嘗味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木同學喜歡秋山同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為  為什麼突然問這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果未來  這樣的生活如此持續下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和奏只不過是普通的青梅竹馬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  難道你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動室裡的紅茶差不多要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該補充一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都能記著真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  愛理回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏說要出去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要買些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以乾脆就出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也想嘗試更多種類的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要去買點材料回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要什麼只要說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就會幫你們買回來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去買也很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就去地下的食品區了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是要買雜貨  大概是在上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KENNY能來這邊幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還提不了重的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要買什麼啊  準備買那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之是很多東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結就過去幫一下奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要好好盯著奏不要浪費錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了我剛才說的要買紅茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要把他們兩個湊到一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒什麼原因的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是活動室裡常喝的那個你精挑細選的紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  馬上就要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是結告訴我  到時候還得特地再過來買
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  這些就齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  和佳織的挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  讓你陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到什麼有意思的東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  這個看起來好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能給我一口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No money
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給我忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的分你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}噢  會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Thanks so  so very very very much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在一起真的很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做個磅蛋糕怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sounds good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責的已經做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就到這裡負責試吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是有多餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫我還處在身體瘋長的階段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去幫秋山同學的忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算去了也沒什麼事幹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那結你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  看上去不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來看看能不能幫你點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山同學你真的很喜歡星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只記得小時候看到的星空漂亮得令我感動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽別人說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在地面上看見的星辰的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前發出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從遙遠的宇宙歷經漫長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才終於抵達這裡的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處女座銀河距離地球是239萬光年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所見到的光是239萬年前的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,239萬年  無論是時間上還是距離上都讓人難以想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個從後面照一下試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還沒有加上顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是夏季的星座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後你想起些什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒必要著急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候總會想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得某個人的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張側臉雖然在微笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻又非常的憂傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是古川的親人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是親人…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太清楚  不過對古川來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是個和你有很深的關聯的人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛才古川說話的時候顯得很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那個人對我來說應該是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一二三等星都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  我是結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡傻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之臨時組裝完之後去看看那邊的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  佳織來過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在說這句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like them all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是會很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  你覺得天象儀真的能吸引來顧客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底  大家期待的只是佳織的女僕裝和親手做的點心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得天文學會的會長說這個是不是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  KENNY偶爾也會說些正經話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪個看上去都很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我姑且也幫了忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華宮學姐也試吃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  什麼都沒能幫到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼  這話凪沙一說聽上去好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是來接結的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是試裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過天象儀也已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  關燈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是奏做出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  底座是KENNY做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的部份結也來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然用名字稱呼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  沒什麼大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  比起這個  還是快看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  那就是夏季大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來天文宅發揮本領了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大三角的織女星雖然看上去是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在夏季南邊天空上天蠍座的心宿二卻被稱為紅超巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發著紅色的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說為什麼會有顏色的區別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為表面溫度的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心宿二大約在3500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的織女星大約是9500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提  太陽的表面溫度大約是6000度左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  謝謝你來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只做到三等星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少在文化節之前能完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過嘛  接下來才是重頭戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更小的四五等星的洞差不多要鑽3000個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等級是依靠光亮來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但實際的亮度和觀測時的亮度還是有區別的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫絕對星等和視星等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個天象儀總之…
